  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Call for Bids: Promoting Societal Links between Gaza & West Bank
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The British Consulate General, Jerusalem is accepting proposals for an 18-month project starting November 2020 under its Conflict, Stability and Security Fund.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 23 September 2020
    <br></br>Last updated 12 October 2020
